{"data":[{"name":"81:1","price":"1. Cuando el sol se oscurezca y su luz se extinga (el Día del Juicio Final);","arabic":"إِذَا ٱلشَّمۡسُ كُوِّرَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5801,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"es"},{"name":"81:2","price":"2. cuando las estrellas se dispersen y caigan (abandonando sus órbitas);","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلنُّجُومُ ٱنكَدَرَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5802,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"es"},{"name":"81:3","price":"3. cuando las montañas sean desplazadas de sus sitios y pulverizadas;","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلۡجِبَالُ سُيِّرَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5803,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"es"},{"name":"81:4","price":"4. cuando las camellas preñadas sean abandonadas;","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلۡعِشَارُ عُطِّلَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5804,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"es"},{"name":"81:5","price":"5. cuando las bestias sean congregadas;","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلۡوُحُوشُ حُشِرَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5805,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"es"},{"name":"81:6","price":"6. cuando los mares ardan;","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلۡبِحَارُ سُجِّرَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5806,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"es"},{"name":"81:7","price":"7. cuando las almas se emparejen[1119]; ","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلنُّفُوسُ زُوِّجَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5807,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"[1119]  Puede significar cuando el alma se reúna con su cuerpo o cuando los piadosos se reúnan con los piadosos y los pecadores con los pecadores.","lang":"es"},{"name":"81:8","price":"8. cuando se les pregunte a las niñas recién nacidas (enterradas vivas)","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلۡمَوۡءُۥدَةُ سُئِلَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5808,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"es"},{"name":"81:9","price":"9. por qué pecado fueron asesinadas[1120];","arabic":"بِأَيِّ ذَنۢبٖ قُتِلَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5809,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"[1120]  Ver la nota de la aleya 137 de la sura 6.","lang":"es"},{"name":"81:10","price":"10. cuando los registros de las obras sean repartidos y abiertos; ","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلصُّحُفُ نُشِرَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5810,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"es"},{"name":"81:11","price":"11. cuando el cielo sea arrancado de su lugar;","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلسَّمَآءُ كُشِطَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5811,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"es"},{"name":"81:12","price":"12. cuando el infierno se avive;","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلۡجَحِيمُ سُعِّرَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5812,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"es"},{"name":"81:13","price":"13. cuando el paraíso se acerque (a quienes vayan a habitarlo);","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلۡجَنَّةُ أُزۡلِفَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5813,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"es"},{"name":"81:14","price":"14. entonces, todos sabrán las buenas y malas acciones que cometieron.","arabic":"عَلِمَتۡ نَفۡسٞ مَّآ أَحۡضَرَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5814,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"es"},{"name":"81:15","price":"15. Juro por los astros que desaparecen (durante el día)","arabic":"فَلَآ أُقۡسِمُ بِٱلۡخُنَّسِ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5815,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"es"},{"name":"81:16","price":"16. y recorren (el cielo) con rapidez (por la noche) y después se ocultan;","arabic":"ٱلۡجَوَارِ ٱلۡكُنَّسِ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5816,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"es"},{"name":"81:17","price":"17. (juro) por la noche cuando llega con su oscuridad","arabic":"وَٱلَّيۡلِ إِذَا عَسۡعَسَ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5817,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"es"},{"name":"81:18","price":"18. y por cuando aclara el día","arabic":"وَٱلصُّبۡحِ إِذَا تَنَفَّسَ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5818,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"es"},{"name":"81:19","price":"19. que el Corán es la palabra (de Al-lah revelada a través) de un mensajero honorable (el ángel Gabriel),","arabic":"إِنَّهُۥ لَقَوۡلُ رَسُولٖ كَرِيمٖ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5819,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"es"},{"name":"81:20","price":"20. el cualha sido dotado de poder y dispone de una posición elevada ante el Señor del Trono,","arabic":"ذِي قُوَّةٍ عِندَ ذِي ٱلۡعَرۡشِ مَكِينٖ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5820,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"es"},{"name":"81:21","price":"21. y es obedecido y respetado (en los cielos por otros ángeles) y digno de confianza.","arabic":"مُّطَاعٖ ثَمَّ أَمِينٖ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5821,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"es"},{"name":"81:22","price":"22. Y (juro que) vuestro compañero (Muhammad) no está loco.","arabic":"وَمَا صَاحِبُكُم بِمَجۡنُونٖ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5822,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"es"},{"name":"81:23","price":"23. Y realmente vio (al ángel Gabriel en su forma original) en el claro horizonte[1121];","arabic":"وَلَقَدۡ رَءَاهُ بِٱلۡأُفُقِ ٱلۡمُبِينِ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5823,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"[1121]  Ver la nota de la aleya 6 de la sura 53.","lang":"es"},{"name":"81:24","price":"24. y no ha ocultado nada de la revelación.","arabic":"وَمَا هُوَ عَلَى ٱلۡغَيۡبِ بِضَنِينٖ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5824,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"es"},{"name":"81:25","price":"25. Y esta exhortación no es la palabra del Demonio, el expulsado.","arabic":"وَمَا هُوَ بِقَوۡلِ شَيۡطَٰنٖ رَّجِيمٖ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5825,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"es"},{"name":"81:26","price":"26. ¿Adónde vais, pues? (¿Qué camino seguiréis si os alejáis del Corán?)","arabic":"فَأَيۡنَ تَذۡهَبُونَ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5826,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"es"},{"name":"81:27","price":"27. En verdad, (el Corán) es una exhortación para los mundos de los hombres y de los yinn,","arabic":"إِنۡ هُوَ إِلَّا ذِكۡرٞ لِّلۡعَٰلَمِينَ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5827,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"es"},{"name":"81:28","price":"28. para quien quiera guiarse de vosotros.","arabic":"لِمَن شَآءَ مِنكُمۡ أَن يَسۡتَقِيمَ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5828,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"es"},{"name":"81:29","price":"29. Y no podréis hacerlo a menos que Al-lah, el Señor de toda la creación, lo quiera.","arabic":"وَمَا تَشَآءُونَ إِلَّآ أَن يَشَآءَ ٱللَّهُ رَبُّ ٱلۡعَٰلَمِينَ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5829,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"es"}],"chapter":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir","Chapter At-Takwir","Takwir","Surah Takwir","Chapter Takwir","At Takwir","Surah At Takwir","Chapter At Takwir","Surah 81","Chapter 81","The Overthrowing","التكوير"]}